.TH PRODBOX_commands 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-commands \- Render the command registry
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox commands
.SH DESCRIPTION
Render the command registry in plain text, tree, or JSON form.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--tree\fR
Render the command registry as a tree
.TP
\fB--json\fR
Render the command registry as JSON
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox commands\fR
Render the command registry in plain-text form.
.TP
\fBprodbox commands --tree\fR
Render the command registry as a tree.
.TP
\fBprodbox commands --json\fR
Render the command registry as JSON.
